{"tid":2396829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄧炳強稱疫情下多了人留在家中網購　令騙徒有機可乘","createTime":"2021-02-06T02:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T02:50:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c77f9fd903996fb0ec8b6cdf81761b1a32b1801a","tid":2396829,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"警務處處長鄧炳強表示，去年本港錄得63000多宗罪案，比前年增加4000多宗，詐騙案佔7000多宗，若撇除詐騙案，整體數字屬下跌。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強在本台節目《星期六問責》表示，網上購物騙案去年增加4000多宗，與口罩有關的佔2000多宗。他說，疫情下很多人留在家中，更多在網上購物或使用社交與交友平台，令騙徒有機可乘。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強說，去年詐騙案整體破案率相對較低，只有11%左右，這類騙案過往破案率亦偏低，前年破案率亦只有13%。他說，調查方面有困難，因為很多時騙徒使用「太空卡」，因此支持有關政策局檢視「太空卡」的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574422-20210206.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574422-20210206.htm&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjKwvV4D0jUJVCqNn8v1PCJE%3D&h=0c2baf82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574422-20210206.htm&h=5a78a8c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574422-20210206.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0e045feb36fb786c10557c3d07b7a08938375e80","tid":2396829,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"冇嘢搵嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 管好你d犯冰冰先"},{"pid":"cfbc1c334ff11fc97aa943743dce67f8e2f9e12f","tid":2396829,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:36:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦戲子"},{"pid":"27accad72b6f8cf76e975b719cfc75ebeb7463ac","tid":2396829,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"成日收到3字頭同海外騙案就多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"887018dc8db7cf54248d32d33a85cfba0fd10c52","tid":2396829,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quot